    >
        <div class="pt-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <p class="font-chelsea text-[#e3be05]">The second outing of Day Drinking Survivor upped the level of competition. With a cast of returning players and a plethora of newbies, this season was the juiciest yet.</p>
